Articles.Content:
so, I have a "few mods" on my ksp save (airplane plus, scifi visual enhancements, kerbal engineer redux, kopernicus, persistent rotation, vens stock revamp, and a few more) all of these mods worked, before I added texture replacer, Distant object enhancement, and a amazing skybox for Texture replacer. As of late, I have been having problems with the ksp "spash"/loading screen crashing at a wing strake from airplane plus. I`m pretty confused as to why this is happening.
